{
  "conceptual": "\n<p sourcefile=\"pages/docs/terrain/terrain-overview.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"3\"><img src=\"~/pages/docs/terrain/media/terrain-overview.jpg\" sourcefile=\"pages/docs/terrain/terrain-overview.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"3\" alt=\"Terrain overview\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"terrain\" sourcefile=\"pages/docs/terrain/terrain-overview.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"5\">Terrain</h2>\n<p sourcefile=\"pages/docs/terrain/terrain-overview.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"7\">ezEngine includes a brush-based <a href=\"~/pages/docs/terrain/terrain-plugin-overview.md\" sourcefile=\"pages/docs/terrain/terrain-overview.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"7\">terrain system</a> for creating heightfield and voxel terrain. Terrain is shaped by placing brush objects in the scene. The system is non-destructive, so brushes can be repositioned or removed at any time.</p>\n<h2 id=\"vegetation\" sourcefile=\"pages/docs/terrain/terrain-overview.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"9\">Vegetation</h2>\n<p sourcefile=\"pages/docs/terrain/terrain-overview.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"11\">Vegetation can be created with standard meshes. Using custom <a href=\"~/pages/docs/materials/visual-shaders.md\" sourcefile=\"pages/docs/terrain/terrain-overview.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"11\">visual shaders</a>, a basic per-vertex wind animation can be applied.</p>\n<p sourcefile=\"pages/docs/terrain/terrain-overview.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"13\">Additionally, ezEngine has built in support for <a href=\"~/pages/docs/terrain/kraut-overview.md\" sourcefile=\"pages/docs/terrain/terrain-overview.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"13\">Kraut</a>, a system for procedurally generating tree meshes.</p>\n<p sourcefile=\"pages/docs/terrain/terrain-overview.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"15\">Finally, there is a <a href=\"~/pages/docs/terrain/procedural/procedural-object-placement.md\" sourcefile=\"pages/docs/terrain/terrain-overview.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"15\">procedural placement system</a> to scatter objects, typically plants, around the current player position.</p>\n<h2 id=\"see-also\" sourcefile=\"pages/docs/terrain/terrain-overview.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"17\">See Also</h2>\n<ul sourcefile=\"pages/docs/terrain/terrain-overview.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"19\">\n<li sourcefile=\"pages/docs/terrain/terrain-overview.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"19\"><a href=\"~/pages/docs/terrain/terrain-plugin-overview.md\" sourcefile=\"pages/docs/terrain/terrain-overview.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"19\">Terrain System</a></li>\n<li sourcefile=\"pages/docs/terrain/terrain-overview.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"20\"><a href=\"~/pages/docs/terrain/procedural/procedural-object-placement.md\" sourcefile=\"pages/docs/terrain/terrain-overview.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"20\">Procedural Object Placement</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
  "type": "Conceptual",
